title: TWO BEDROOM CONDO AVAILABLE FOR IMMEDIATE OCCUPANCY!
app_fee: $40.00 application fee for credit/criminal background checks and processing
posting_body: ['Great location on spacious two bedroom, one full bath condominium near Leetsdale and Quebec across the street from Fairmount, with easy access to downtown or the Denver Tech Center and just south of the new shops and restaurants at Boulevard One and the Lowry Town Center.', 'Two generous bedrooms, one full bathroom, and spacious living room that includes fireplace, and sliding patio door that leads to outside deck for relaxing.', ' Kitchen features refrigerator, range/oven, microwave oven, dishwasher, and full-size washer and dryer in laundry closet!', ' One reserved parking space is included, and there is ample additional guest parking as well.', ' A convenient separate private storage unit is also included for storing your extra toys!', 'Water, sewer, trash, and exterior maintenance are included in the rent!', 'Parks, shopping and schools are within easy walking distance.', 'Section 8 Tenants are welcome to apply!', '$40.00 rental application fee.', " Security deposit is equal to one month's rent.", '**Upon initial contact, please share some basic information about yourself and any others that would be living with you, including type of employment, pets if any, and your desired lease start date.', ' No showings will be set until we have this basic information.']
